  "detailed_description": "Jigsaw puzzle fun - on your own, with friends and family, or make new puzzle pals from around the world! Choose from millions of beautiful images of all kinds, upload your own pictures for custom puzzles, or create any puzzle you can imagine by simply describing it. Voice chat lets you feel like you're all sitting around the same table. Automatically sort pieces by edges or color. Features 3D pieces and physics for a realistic puzzle-making experience!",
  "about_the_game": "Jigsaw puzzle fun - on your own, with friends and family, or make new puzzle pals from around the world! Choose from millions of beautiful images of all kinds, upload your own pictures for custom puzzles, or create any puzzle you can imagine by simply describing it. Voice chat lets you feel like you're all sitting around the same table. Automatically sort pieces by edges or color. Features 3D pieces and physics for a realistic puzzle-making experience!",
